# Components Structure

The application uses a structured component system for UI elements:

## UI Components

- [src/components/ui](mdc:src/components/ui) - Contains UI component library elements

## Feature Components

- [src/components/ThemeSwitcher](mdc:src/components/ThemeSwitcher) - Theme switching functionality
- [src/components/TitleBadge](mdc:src/components/TitleBadge) - Badge components for titles
- [src/components/PanelParticles](mdc:src/components/PanelParticles) - Particle effects for panels
- [src/components/MotionWrapper](mdc:src/components/MotionWrapper) - Animation wrappers using Framer Motion
- [src/components/HomepageHero](mdc:src/components/HomepageHero) - Hero section for homepage
- [src/components/CustomFooter](mdc:src/components/CustomFooter) - Footer components

## Widgets and Higher-Level Components

- [src/widgets](mdc:src/widgets) - Higher-level components that may combine multiple smaller components

